high_descs: walk over to the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
grab the black plate off of the counter
turn and walk a bit over to the microwave
place the black plate inside the microwave, turn it on and then take it out once it's done
walk on over to the brown shelves in the corner of the kitchen
place the hot plate on the top shelf of the brown shelves
anns.task_desc: place a hot plate on top of the shelves in the corner of the kitchen

high_descs: Turn right, then turn left, then go straight and turn right; go to the stove.
Pick up the dish on the counter, in front of the toaster.
Go to the right, toward the stove.
Heat the dish in the microwave above the stove.
Turn around and go right, then turn left, then right, toward the shelf against the wall.
Place the dish on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm dish on a shelf.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Bring the plate to the microwave.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Bring the heated plate to the wooden rack.
Put the heated plate on the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate on the wooden rack.
